          "level": 2,
          "type": "heading",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "text": "Overview"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "RealityKit simulates physical interactions between virtual objects in your scene, as well as between virtual objects and detected surfaces in the real world, such as floors, walls, or tabletops.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "On devices with a LiDAR Scanner, RealityKit can even simulate interactions between virtual objects and scanned real-world geometry.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
